---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy & Analytics | Vincenzo Di Perna"
  description="Privacy and analytics information for Vincenzo Di Perna's personal website."
  sideBarActiveItemID="contact"
>
  <section class="mb-8">
    <div class="network-protected card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy & analytics</h1>

        <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90">
          This personal website uses privacy-conscious analytics to understand
          aggregate traffic and improve its research, project, tutorial, and CV
          sections.
        </p>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">What is measured</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90 mt-2">
          The site may collect aggregate information such as page views, referrers,
          approximate location, device/browser information, and selected interaction
          events such as CV download clicks, GitHub or Zenodo link clicks, email link
          clicks, and interactions with the CryptoEntropy Explorer.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6">What is not measured</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90 mt-2">
          The site does not use login accounts, does not ask visitors to create a
          profile, and does not intentionally collect names, email addresses, or
          personal identifiers through analytics.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6">Analytics provider</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90 mt-2">
          Analytics are implemented with PostHog Cloud EU and configured for
          cookieless tracking. Session recording is disabled. The analytics setup is
          used only to evaluate how the website content and interactive tools are used.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6">Contact</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90 mt-2">
          For questions about this website or its analytics setup, contact me from the
          <a class="link link-primary" href="/contact">Contact me</a> page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
